### 6. Non-goals / Out of scope
- **Promotions system** (legacy credits) — only product trials for now
- **Self-hosted Sentry** — the `/customers/` endpoint is getsentry-specific (SaaS); self-hosted won't have it. The `getSeerTrialStatus` call will 404 gracefully → falls through to normal error.
- **Caching trial status** — Keep it simple; check fresh each time (these errors are rare).

